<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.9.3">
<l>oruvaṉai yuntip pūmē lōṅkuvit tākan taṉṉāl</l>
<l>oruvaṉaic cāpam nīkki yumparā ḷeṉṟu viṭṭāṉ</l>
<l>peruvarai matiḷkaḷ cūḻnta perunaka rarava ṇaimēl</l>
<l>karuvarai vaṇṇaṉ taṉpēr karutinā ṉuynta vāṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The way I was saved was by reflecting on the name of the one who,</l>
<l>Having raised one up on the flower of his navel and having removed a curse</l>
<l>For one with his chest, saying, “Rule the heavens,” gave [him] leave,</l>
<l>The one with the hue of a dark mountain on a serpent couch in the great city</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by huge mountain-like walls.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
